---
import GoalsImg from "../../public/images/goals.webp";
import UnderlineWord from "./UnderlineWord.astro";
---

<section class="goals py-5">
	<div class="container px-4 py-5">
		<h2 class="pb-2 font-poppins position-relative title-underline">
			Nuestros 
            <UnderlineWord word="objetivos"/>
		</h2>
		<p class="w50 mt-4">
			Nos ocupamos de la comercialización, operación y el mantenimiento
			tanto preventivo como correctivo del establecimiento.
		</p>
		<div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2">
			<div class="feature col mb-3">
				<div
					class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3"
				>
					<svg
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						stroke-width="1.5"
						stroke="currentColor"
						width="1em"
						height="1em"
					>
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h4 class="text-body-emphasis mt-3">Gestión inmobiliaria</h4>
				<p class="w75">
					De operaciones relacionadas con el alquiler de tus
					propiedades, encontrar inquilinos confiables y asegurar un
					flujo constante de ingresos.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature col mb-3">
				<div
					class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3"
				>
					<svg
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						stroke-width="1.5"
						stroke="currentColor"
						width="1em"
						height="1em"
					>
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							d="M9 12h3.75M9 15h3.75M9 18h3.75m3 .75H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6.108c0-1.135-.845-2.098-1.976-2.192a48.424 48.424 0 0 0-1.123-.08m-5.801 0c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0 1 13.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m0 0H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.375c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H8.25ZM6.75 12h.008v.008H6.75V12Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V15Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V18Z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h4 class="text-body-emphasis mt-3">Gestión comercial</h4>
				<p class="w75">
					Contamos con experiencia en el rubro hotelero. Estamos
					profesionalmente preparados para brindarte el asesoramiento
					necesario.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature col mb-3">
				<div
					class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3"
				>
					<svg
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						stroke-width="1.5"
						stroke="currentColor"
						width="1em"
						height="1em"
					>
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							d="M10.5 6a7.5 7.5 0 1 0 7.5 7.5h-7.5V6Z"></path>
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							d="M13.5 10.5H21A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 13.5 3v7.5Z"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h4 class="text-body-emphasis mt-3">Gestión integral</h4>
				<p class="w75">
					Optimización de procesos operativos junto con la promoción
					del bienestar de nuestros colaboradores, asegurando el
					compromiso con la calidad y responsabilidad ambiental.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature col mb-3">
				<img
					src={GoalsImg.src}
					alt="Objetivos"
					class="goals-image d-block mx-auto mx-lg-0"
					loading="lazy"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.goals {
		background-color: var(--lt-grey);
	}
    .goals .title-underline {
        width: fit-content;
    }
	.goals .feature {
		min-height: 14rem;
	}
	.goals .feature .feature-icon {
		width: 3rem;
		height: 3rem;
		color: var(--white);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		background-color: var(--st-orange);
	}
	@media screen and (max-width: 991px) {
		.goals .feature .goals-image {
			width: 75%;
			height: auto;
			object-fit: contain;
		}
	}
</style>
